    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {className: a3; margin-bottom: 6pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a5 {font-family: 'Times New Roman';}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаролик ишлар бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган фуқаролик суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> судига</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#5}Ариза берувчининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 311.86703601108px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 324.43213296399px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#6}Ариза берувчи шахснинг Ф.И.Ш.и </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">дан</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Фуқаролик иш бўйича иш юритишни тугатиш тўғрисида</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Фуқаролик ишлар бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#2}Ариза берилган фуқаролик суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> судининг иш юритувида жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#8}Иш бўйича жавогарнинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">га нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#9}Даъво ариза мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> ҳақидаги даъво аризам юзасидан юритилган фуқаролик иши мавжуд. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Бугунги кунга келиб, даъво аризамда қайд этилган низо юзасидан жавобгар билан ўртамиздаги келишмовчиликлар бартараф этилган. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик процессуал Кодексининг <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>124-моддасига кўра,</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> даъвогар арз қилинган талабларидан воз кечган ва суд бу воз кечишни қабул қилган бўлса иш юритиш тугатилади. </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Мазкур кодекснинг 125-моддасига кўра, <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">иш юритиш суднинг ажрими билан тугатилади. Агар иш юритиш иш судга тааллуқли бўлмаганлиги сабабли тугатилса ва низони ҳал этиш бошқа давлат органининг ваколатига тааллуқли бўлса, суд аризачининг қайси органга мурожаат қилиши кераклигини кўрсатиши шарт.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Мен юқоридагилардан келиб чиққан ҳолда жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#8}Иш бўйича жавогарнинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">га нисбатан бўлган даъво талабларимдан воз кечаман.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Даъво талабларидан воз кечишнинг ҳуқуқий оқибатлари менга суд томонидан тушунтирилган. <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 47.2px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">Юқоридагилардан келиб чиқиб, Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик процессуал кодекснинг 42, 43, 157-моддасига асосланиб, мени жавобгар </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#8}Иш бўйича жавогарнинг Ф.И.Оси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">га нисбатан </span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">{#9}Даъво ариза мазмуни</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> тўғрисидаги даъво талабларимдан воз кечганлигимни қабул қилиб, иш юритишни тугатишингизни.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#6}Ариза берувчи шахснинг Ф.И.Ш.и </span></p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.07756232687px;\">\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">имзо</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 212.14404432133px;\">\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: right; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#3}Ариза берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> йил</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n</div></div>",
